SQL JDBC in  EMR

Download driver from : https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/sql/connect/jdbc/download-microsoft-jdbc-driver-for-sql-server?view=sql-server-ver15

Copy mssql-jdbc-8.2.0.jre8 to EMR instance (eg:./)

sudo nano /etc/spark/conf/spark-defaults.conf

add the downloaded driver path to : spark.driver.extraClassPath and spark.executor.extraClassPath

Restart Kernel!

